The 2019 Data Storage, Backup and Recovery Conference will take place on 13 March 2019 at The Venue in Melrose Arch. The conference will feature top speakers who will cover a wide range of topics, including data storage, disaster recovery, digital transformation, Microsoft Cloud in SA, and data protection. The delegates will also be able to interact with South Africa’s best Data Storage, Backup and Recovery companies during the networking breaks. The emcee for the event is Radio 702’s Aki Anastasiou, who will be joined by top industry experts as speakers. Sponsors for the conference include Commvault, Gabsten Technologies, VMWare, and ContinuitySA. MyBroadband readers can buy a ticket to the conference at a discounted price using the voucher code below. Please note that only 55 tickets are still available for the event at this discounted price, and these seats will be allocated on a first-come-first-served basis.